Ask HN: How long do people go on Xmas leave in your region?
text:
People have already started going on leaves for a month and more. As a startup/tech person, it takes me time to wrap my head around such long leaves.

How long people go for leaves in your region? How much off-time do you take?

Just curious, no judgements!
